{% set daylight = 1 %}
{% if daylight %}
<div class="content gradeable_message daylight" id="daylight" style="margin-bottom: 1em;">
    <p>
        WARNING: Daylight savings is THIS WEEK! Please note that a late day is 24 HOURS.
        <br>
        This means that if an assignment is due at 10 pm a day BEFORE daylight savings in the spring, and you plan to use a late day, you must submit your assignment before 10 pm, at the latest 9:59 PM.
        <br>
        As for when an assignment is due at 10 pm a day AFTER daylight savings ends in the fall, you must submit your assignment by 11 pm.
    </p>
</div>
{% endif %}